[assistant] Implemented test refinements for `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Changes:
[assistant] - Added `ConnectorProtocolIntrospectionTest.java`
[assistant]   - Exercises `Connector.getProperty(...)` through Tomcat’s public API.
[assistant]   - Covers protocol property introspection for:
[assistant]     - `name` → reflectively invokes `AbstractProtocol.getName()`
[assistant]     - unknown property → falls back to `AbstractProtocol.getProperty(String)`
[assistant]     - `SSLEnabled` → reflectively invokes `AbstractHttp11Protocol.isSSLEnabled()`
[assistant]   - Runs against `HTTP/1.1`, `Http11NioProtocol`, and `Http11Nio2Protocol`.
[assistant]   - Uses port `0` and cleans up connector lifecycle.
[assistant] 
[assistant] - Refined `TomcatTests.java`
[assistant]   - Switched from fixed port `8080` to auto-bind port `0`.
[assistant]   - Re-checks protocol introspection after Tomcat startup.
[assistant]   - Builds request URI from `connector.getLocalPort()`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] No metadata files were edited, and I did not run tests locally per instructions.
